From: Paolo D'Urso <darkage@idealia.net>

The new version (2.0) of Extreme is out! Registered users or owners of previous
versions will be able to run it just using their keyfile, all the others can run
this program as demo version (some features disabled). News in this update are
bugfixes here and there, up and down; many things has improved since v1.50;
however, development hasn't stopped yet (except if we'll find too many cracked
copies around)!

