stupid bug with with the screenmode requester and it should be overall more
stable.

You can download both updates from http://www.darkage.it and from Aminet
(biz/dkg).

Extreme is a powerful realtime generator of background effects for video
productions. Enjoy a new dimension in the world of videotitling! Tunnels, Waves,
Rain effects will be easy and fast to create, with only few clicks of the mouse.
It features:

   - 100% Assembler code;
